<item>
            <title>[LU-4999] lustre_idl.h compilation regression from LU-3569</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4999</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Patch da12d3ba for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3569&quot; title=&quot;Use real OST index as ostid_to_fid() parameter instead of always &amp;quot;0&amp;quot;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3569&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3569&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; introduced a regression into lustre_idl.h.  lustre_idl.h is packaged for inclusion in userspace, and therefore cannot use parts from lustre&apos;s kernel internals.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CERROR is not permitted in lustre_idl.h.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
